textAnnotations.description:
Durable plastic-alloy jacketing helps
protect neck from fraying and splintering
if incorrectly struck or overstruck.
Hammers
Polished, forged,
tempered-steel head.
Comfortable, perforated neoprene
grip bonded to handle.
KERIN
High-strength fiberglass shaft
absorbs shock and keeps head tight.
MADE IN USA
